article_title: U.S. attorney nomination for New Mexico goes to Senate
article_text:

og.description: If he can make it through the U.S. Senate approval process, a federal prosecutor in Albuquerque with decades of legal experience, particularly in prosecuting organized crime, will be the next U.S. attorney for New Mexico.
